{# Looking for Work

{% if metadata.available == true %}

	<section class="section section--available-for-work section--is-inset">

		<header class="section__header">

			<h2 class="section__title">Looking for Work</h2>

		</header>

		<div class="section__content">

			<p>I'm currently on the lookout for new job opportunities that match my skill set and professional goals. This search is driven by my eagerness to join forward-thinking teams and projects where I can contribute significantly and enhance my career growth, making a positive difference along the way.</p>

		</div>

	</section>

